features: [Bookshelf With Cabinet Design]: The tall bookcase has a back panel design than the standard open bookcase, which makes the industrial bookshelf more integral. It also allows the freestanding bookshelf to be placed off the wall without worrying about items falling off the back, making it more practical and more aesthetically pleasing.

[Stable And Durable Large Bookshelf]: This bookcase is made of high-quality steel and MDF board. In contrast, the stable side steel tube frame and overall connecting fittings give the tier bookshelves a high degree of stability and quality. 4 adjustable foot pads make this 6-shelf bookshelf accommodate uneven floors and protect your floor from damage during movement.

[Suitable Size For Great Display]: The overall dimensions of the tall bookcases are 23.62(W)*11.81(D)*70.94(H), with a height of 12.5 inches between the bookshelves, allowing this display rack to provide spacious storage and display space. Fill the spacious display shelves with your favorites! Choose the best display bookcase for your books, plants, CDs, magazines, and collectibles! Maximum weight capacity: 70 lbs/32 kg per shelf.

[Multifunctional Bookshelf]: The unique side design of this home bookcase is combined with vintage wood grain to adapt to different styles of furniture. The simple upright and open book shelf can help you to save more indoor space. You can use the modern bookshelf for bedroom, living room, study, office or corner. At the same time, the 6 shelf has a scratch-resistant, impact-resistant, waterproof design, which can protect the surface from daily wear and tear.

[Professional Installation Process]: The open bookshelf comes with a professional installation step-by-step manual, which already comes with installation tools and numbered accessories to help you get it done easily within an hour! If you still have any questions about vintage bookshelves, please feel free to contact us, we will be in the first time!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Ease and Elegance
reviews.reviewText: Simple assembly. (Just don’t rush it!). Very functional and attractive. Stronger than anticipated, too. Yay! Quality and good looks.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Well built - looks great
reviews.reviewText: I have done many flat pack put together before and this is one of the easiest I've ever done. All simple screws. No funky ways to join it together just straightforward screws. There are front in the back to the metal pieces so be sure you have all of the holes on the correct side. And the top it has a front and a back. The rest of the shelves are so well finished all sides are finished so it doesn't matter which is front and back or top or bottom for the shelves. Both front feet are adjustable so no wiggling. I didn't need to adjust the back feet, I think that they are adjustable but I can't say for sure. Very stable when it goes together no wiggling. I got it together by myself in about an hour. It would definitely be easier and faster with two people probably would take 20 minutes. The back instead of being a flimsy cardboard thing that gets nailed on is actually thicker and get screwed on as well. Super simple to put together. Was well packaged. Arrived with no damage. Shelves are nice thick definitely will hold my books without sagging. Whatever the Finish is on these it does not appear to be thin paper but some sort of hard laminate. It looks like it should hold up well and it looks like real wood. Was also provided with one to two extra screws per type of screw. I didn't need them but it's always nice for that one that the cat helps you lose. This was a great deal. I could not have purchased wood and built one for this price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Quality, Easy to Assemble
reviews.reviewText: I usually dont order things like furniture that I cant physically see in person. But I needed a shelf to fit a specific wall for a collection of mine. The shelf came in 1 box and was a bit heavy but I could get it in the house. I assembled by myself and the instructions are very simple. It was easy to put together and you don't need additional tools to assemble. Everything you need is in the package. The shelf is very sturdy and I think for what Im using it for it will last a very long time. I like so much I will be ordering a second one right away. I highly recommend!
